    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and never missed a service. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
