    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This vehicle exhibits flawless mechanical synchronization, having undergone a proactive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to exceed factory durability standards. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a meticulously maintained suspension geometry and OEM forged alloys. Every component, from the limited-slip differential to the high-pressure fuel rail, operates at peak performance parameters. Aesthetically preserved and mechanically superlative, this is a turnkey example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
